<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12114a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12114a">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12114a"> 114(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ cough in church / smile &mdash; &mdash; / sing false / not bow (6</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Celui qui toussait au commencement de l&apos;office ou ne chantait pas bien, recevait six coups de verges, comme celui qui souriait &agrave; l&apos;&eacute;glise ou ne s&apos;inclinait point &agrave; la fin de chaque psaume. <br> <font color="green">[He who coughs at the start of the service or does not sing well, receives six blows of the rod, like he who smiles in church or does not bow at the end of each psalm.]</font> <small> <a name="STCM" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#STCM"><cite title="source">Saint Colomban</cite></a> (1905) 60</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
